; KK-MasterVP XAUUSD M5 — H9-C VALIDATION (progressive-trail LATE-ARM ladder candidate).
; BASE = deployed M5 lock; ONLY change = ProgTrail ON at the MT5-optimizer winner:
;   InpPmProgTrail=true / TriggerR=2.0 (arm LATE) / IncrementR=0.75 / StepR=0.2.
; MT5 36-pass optimizer (real ticks, 2025.06.01-2026.05.29): 90,781 net / PF 1.448 / DD 14.5% / 1425 tr,
;   vs lock 87,838 / PF 1.436 / DD 14.5% — beats lock on PF + net + DD, same entries (pure exit gain).
; RUN 3x on KK-MasterVP, XAUUSD, M5, 'Every tick based on real ticks', deposit 10000, single pass:
;   (1) FULL 2025.06.01->2026.05.29  (2) 2025.06.01->2025.12.31  (3) 2026.01.01->2026.05.29.
;   InpExportParity=true -> trades_*.csv feeds research/stats/gate.py.  Must beat lock on BOTH sub-folds.
;
